com.here.platform.location.dataloader.core

Interface DataLoader<Id,T>

  • Type Parameters:
    Id - Key type used to load data with this loader.
    T - The type of data loaded.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CachingDataLoader<Id,T>, CachingTileLoader<T>, TileLoader<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDataLoaderDecorator, AbstractTileLoaderDecorator, com.here.platform.location.dataloader.core.AbstractTileLoaderDecorator, com.here.platform.location.dataloader.core.internal.BaseTileLoader, LRUCachingDataLoader, LRUCachingTileLoader, StandaloneByteArrayTileLoader, com.here.platform.location.dataloader.core.TransformingTileLoader, TransformingTileLoader
    Deprecated. 
    Use methods based on OptimizedMapLayers instead. Since SDK 2.54.

    An abstract loader type.
